\c 5
\s Kudamwa kwaPetro nevamwe
\p
\v 1 Zvino zvakaitika kuti chaunga chakati chichimumbandidzira kuti vanzwe shoko raMwari, iye akamira parutivi rwegungwa reGenesareti;
\v 2 akaona zvikepe zviviri zvimire parutivi rwegungwa; asi varedzi vakange vabuda mazviri vachisuka mimbure.
\v 3 Akapinda mune chimwe chezvikepe chaiva chaSimoni, akakumbira kwaari kuti abve pavhu zvishoma. Ndokubva agara pasi, akadzidzisa zvaunga ari muchikepe.
\p
\v 4 Zvino wakati amira kutaura, akati kuna Simoni: Pinda kwakadzika udzikise mimbure yenyu kuti ubate.
\v 5 Simoni akapindura, akati kwaari: Tenzi, tafondoka usiku hwose hwakazara, tikasabata chinhu, asi zvamadaro, ndichadzikisa mumbure.
\v 6 Vakati vaita izvozvi, vakakomba dutu rehove zhinji; mumbure wavo ukange wobvaruka.
\v 7 Vakaninira vamwe vavo vakange vari mune chimwe chikepe, kuti vauye vazovabatsira; vakauya vakazadza zvikepe zviri zviviri, zvekuti zvakatanga kunyura.
\v 8 Zvino Simoni Petro wakati achiona, akawira pasi pamabvi aJesu, achiti: Ibvai kwandiri, Ishe, nekuti ndiri munhu mutadzi.
\v 9 Nekuti kushamisika kwakange kwamubata, nevose vakange vanaye, nekubatwa kwehove dzavakange vabata;
\v 10 saizvozvowo Jakobho naJohwani, vanakomana vaZebhedhi, vaiva vadyidzani naSimoni. Jesu ndokuti kuna Simoni: Usatya, kubva zvino ucharedza vanhu.
\v 11 Zvino, vakati vaisa zvikepe kunyika, vakasiya zvose vakamutevera.
\s Jesu unoporesa munhu unamaperembudzi
\p
\v 12 Zvino zvakaitika, ari kune rimwe remaguta, tarira, murume azere maperembudzi; wakati achiona Jesu akawa nechiso, ndokumugombetedza, achiti: Ishe, kana muchida, munogona kundinatsa.
\v 13 Ndokubva atambanudza ruoko, akamubata, achiti: Ndinoda, chinatswa. Pakarepo maperembudzi akabva kwaari.
\v 14 Iye akamuraira kuti asaudza munhu; \add akati\add*: Asi enda undozviratidza kumupristi, ubayire pakunatswa kwako, Mozisi sezvaakaraira, chive chapupu kwavari.
\v 15 Asi shoko pamusoro pake rakanyanya kupararira; zvaunga zvikuru zvikaungana kuzonzwa, nekuporeswa naye pazvifo zvavo.
\v 16 Asi iye waienda kumarenje achinonyengetera.
\s Jesu unoporesa munhu wakafa mitezo
\p
\v 17 Zvino zvakaitika nerimwe ramazuva, iye paakange achidzidzisa; zvino vaFarisi nevadzidzisi vemurairo vakange vagere\add po\add*, vaibva kumisha yese yeGarirea neJudhiya neJerusarema; nesimba raIshe rakange riri\add po\add* kuvaporesa.
\v 18 Uye tarira, varume vakange vakatakura munhu pauchanja wakange akafa mitezo; vakatsvaka kumupinza vaise pamberi pake.
\v 19 Zvino, vakati vachishaiwa pavangamupinza napo nekuda kwechaunga, vakakwira padenga peimba, vakamuburusira pasi pakati neuchanja \add hwake\add*, nemumapfuriro pamberi paJesu.
\v 20 Iye wakati aona rutendo rwavo, akati kwaari: Munhu, zvivi zvako wazvikangamwirwa.
\v 21 Zvino vanyori nevaFarisi vakatanga kufunga, vachiti: Ndiani uyu unotaura kunyomba? Ndiani unogona kukangamwira zvivi, kunze kwaMwari oga?
\v 22 Zvino Jesu paakaziva mifungo yavo, akapindura, akati kwavari: Munofungei mumoyo yenyu?
\v 23 Chii chakareruka, kuti: Zvivi zvako wazviregererwa; kana kuti: Simuka, ufambe?
\v 24 Asi kuti muzive kuti Mwanakomana wemunhu une simba panyika rekuregerera zvivi (akati kune wakange akafa mitezo): Ndinoti kwauri: Simuka, utore uchanja hwako, uende kumba kwako.
\v 25 Pakarepo akasimuka pamberi pavo, akatora chaakange avete pachiri, akaenda kumba kwake, achirumbidza Mwari.
\v 26 Kuvhiringidzika kukabata vose, vakarumbidza Mwari, vakazadzwa nekutya, vachiti: Taona chisionekwe nhasi.
\s Kudamwa kwaRevhi
\p
\v 27 Zvino shure kwezvinhu izvi wakabuda, akaona muteresi, wainzi Revhi, agere paimba yemutero, akati kwaari: Nditevere.
\v 28 Ndokubva asiya zvose, akasimuka akamutevera.
\v 29 Revhi ndokumuitira mabiko makuru mumba make; kukavapo chaunga chikuru chavateresi nevamwe vakange vagere navo pakudya.
\v 30 Asi vanyori vavo nevaFarisi vakanyunyutira vadzidzi vake, vachiti: Nemhaka yei muchidya nekunwa nevateresi nevatadzi?
\v 31 Jesu achipindura akati kwavari: Vakagwinya havadi murapi, asi avo vanorwara.
\v 32 Handina kuuya kuzodana vakarurama, asi vatadzi vauye mukutendeuka.
\s Kutsanya
\p
\v 33 Zvino vakati kwaari: Nemhaka yei vadzidzi vaJohwani vachitsanya kazhinji, vachiita minyengetero, uye saizvozvo vevaFarisi, asi venyu vanodya nekunwa?
\v 34 Asi wakati kwavari: Munogona kutsanyisa vana veimba yemuchato muwani achiri kwavari here?
\v 35 Asi mazuva achasvika, apo muwani achabviswa kwavari, ipapo vachatsanya nemazuva iwayo.
\p
\v 36 Akataurawo mufananidzo kwavari, akati: Hakuna munhu unoisa chigamba chemucheka mutsva panguvo sharu; kana zvakasadaro naichowo chitsva chinobvarura, nechigamba che\add mucheka\add* mutsva hachipindirani nesharu.
\v 37 Uye hakuna munhu unodira waini itsva muhombodo sharu; kana zvakasadaro, waini itsva ichaparusa hombodo iyo ikateuka, uye hombodo dzikaparara.
\v 38 Asi waini itsva inofanira kuiswa muhombodo itsva, zvichengetedzeke zviri zviviri.
\v 39 Uye hakuna munhu unoti kana amwa \add waini\add* sharu pakarepo akashuva itsva; nekuti unoti: Sharu iri nani.
